com.github.jessemull.microflex.bigintegerflex.math

Class MathOperationBigIntegerUnary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jessemull.microflex.bigintegerflex.math.MathOperationBigIntegerUnary
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ComplimentBigInteger, DecrementBigInteger, IncrementBigInteger

    public abstract class MathOperationBigIntegerUnary
extends java.lang.Object
    This class performs mathematical operations with a single argument for BigInteger plate stacks, plates, wells and well sets. To create a custom mathematical operation extend this class and override the calculate methods using the appropriate operation. Unary operations can also be performed on a subset of data using a beginning index and subset length.

    MicroFlex currently supports the following unary mathematical operations for BigInteger objects:
    Operations
    Increment
    Decrement
    Compliment
    Author:
    Jesse L. Mull
